  "instructions": [
    "Heat sesame oil in a large clay pot or Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and sliced ginger and cook until fragrant.",
    "Add fish sauce, soy sauce, and brown sugar, and stir to combine.",
    "Add thawed prawns and cook until they start to turn pink.",
    "Add black pepper and water, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in chopped scallions and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Remove from heat and let cool slightly before serving."
